Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}憧憬之路：在竹原市街道保護區一代，是為了還原江戶時代的繁榮景象而用竹筒裡放著的蠟燭做成的燈裝飾的街道。\N每年都會舉辦賞燈活動，使用的竹筒燈達到3000個之多。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這座城市被竹燈包圍著的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前父親帶著我去的時候  從前一天開始就興奮不已了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是這麼記得的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知為什麼  回憶變得有些模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年在久違了的憧憬之路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會產生怎樣的情愫呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.66,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,100)\fad(500,500)}「因為是竹燈的約定」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備進行得有條不紊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待晚上啊  對吧  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣會不會變糟呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰親  你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去HOBORO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉  馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？  真心好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個姐姐剛做到一半就被叫出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你們所見  是放晴娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起大小  它的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祈願「放晴吧」的祈禱師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  怎麼看都是臨終痛苦的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的薰親看上去完全就是在殺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對小啪來說是久違了的憧憬之路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就說絕對希望天氣放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來做個放晴娘吧什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你父親一起去過之後就再也沒有去過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不如我們也來做個放晴娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也想做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就去找點布料來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小啪今天就是第三次了嘍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是之前的經歷記得不是很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  感覺記憶好像有點模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是當時睏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天一天被姐姐拉著滑草坪啊玩探險啊什麼的  到處轉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到的時候小啪已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因為太期待了前一晚根本睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有小啪親的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早上收拾工作已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法忘記看到如此景象而一臉失落的小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  那時候我和爸爸約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「下次來的時候要看最最美麗的憧憬之路」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那之後爸爸工作很忙  沒有時間來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定…終究沒有實現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  是因為不甘心？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次想要給小啪一個愉快的憧憬之路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  想給你看看最棒的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你昨晚有沒有好好睡著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是完全睡不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  順道去趟Maestro那行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣啊  有什麼推薦的地點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  墓地怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就說「呀  好可怕啊」  然後緊緊抱住對方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話這樣一發就搞定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墳墓上有點燈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  但是暗的地方比較浪漫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒有來這裡問的必要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在暗處抱緊然後親一個也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  你打算告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  紀惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在點著燈的地方趁勢告白的作戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然告白就是應該女生來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是有型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是結果會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了  快到碰頭時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝Good  luck！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也朝HOBORO前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小啪你的事辦完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  我是要來買膠卷的啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  飄起了蠟燭點燃的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音用聲音  薰親用氣味在感受著祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠我剛才開始就在用肚子感受ing啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是動就會照糊了  保持住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這也是照糊ing了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動  求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然還是會照糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用三腳架拍比較好拍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志…志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有多準備一個  你就拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要說的話  算是私事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說憧憬之路很漂亮  就來看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在晚上的點燈開始前  我們去吃什錦燒怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在正要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好開心  正好有點餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你推薦HOBORO燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼堂鄉在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要直呼老師的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒禮貌的傢伙…紅葉饅頭還是白豆餡的最好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  請給我醬汁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位馬上就空出來了…馬鈴薯是配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地笑話更加肆無忌憚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說到了晚上真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望天會放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}即大久野島：位於瀨戶內海，芸予諸島之一，被稱為「地圖上消失的島」或「毒氣之島」\N據說是太平洋戰爭時製造化學武器的島嶼。另外近年來因為大量兔子在島上生息，又被稱為「兔兒島」。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去兔兒島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於實現約定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  我想你一定很中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把沙彌也叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就帶她來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都各自滿懷著心願來到了這個祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家今天都能留下美妙的回憶就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看好你們  想要拜託你們一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看好的地方讓人覺得好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上呢…那個  總之就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想對店主做愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要吵  我做掉你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從很遠的地方來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從東京來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是個好地方  請盡情享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  你們叫她出來散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就來當領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在氣氛不錯的地方你們就全部消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不從一開始就靠自己去邀請啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  要是做得到我還會拜託你們這些傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你們這些」大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被拖下水了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  謝謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於堂鄉老師來說  今天也是特別的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰成功與否就看你們的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以短信為信號  然後你們要在三分鐘之內到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這些傢伙要我教她們人生方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對於這座城市來說是特別之日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家都能綻放笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下起雨來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停快停快停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐明明都做了避雨的咒符呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是弄錯成祈雨詛咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去問問情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的雨還弄得成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…弄得成  雖然很想這麼說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是暫且就等到5點再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還沒停的話就沒辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  我們可都掛了放晴娘了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸給佐代美姐姐的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她也並沒有詛咒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  為什麼偏偏是今天下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  小薰  我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年看不成明年也還能看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒  大家去寫許願燈籠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真是個好提議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪你寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  希望雨能夠停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小啪親的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許更大的願也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說雨不停的話這個也掛不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…希望香親能做我們家小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太心術不正了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了呢  還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還好  有多久沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回來看看久違的憧憬之路的  下雨了真是超打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  難道你是小啪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我…我是澤渡楓  那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計小啪不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有在一起玩過一次的哦  廣野昌子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪是今年春天搬過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌子小姐現在是在東京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又搬家了  現在在橫須賀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫須賀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是一個衣笠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前住在汐入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  好近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常去不入斗公園玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也經常去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有弓道場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}橫須賀某條坡道的愛稱，連接汐入地區和坂本、不入斗地區。愛稱的來由是舊日本陸軍的橫須賀炮兵聯隊進駐\N不入斗地區時士兵們去汐入的娛樂街遊玩，為了回來的時候不遲到而登上這條坡道而來。\N日語裡「遲到」和「千石」同音。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道千石坂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我家離那裡很近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這超絕本地對話算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到這裡來果然還是因為爸爸的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個開朗的爸爸  我還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還和孩子們一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是昌子小姐搬走之後的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是因為調整好心情了  才能來到這個城市的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是雨能停就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是整個小鎮都點滿竹燈  一定從天國也能望見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在燈籠上寫上思念的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得一定能夠傳達到在天國裡的人身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這樣覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼難得的機會  我是不是也要來寫個燈籠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去那邊寫了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  稍微有點害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也繼續寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經四點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺街上的人都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐滿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面現在是空的  請進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  暫時還應付得過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  香親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親  等下一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  愛管閒事的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  會給別的客人添麻煩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要當跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  我是來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑  快交代你的真實目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的目的  那可是…時機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你不要來打擾  因為我喜歡香君嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  被聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你是男孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大嬸做你女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當今社會果然都是女人告白的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她昨晚根本沒怎麼睡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是小啪回來後第一次的憧憬之路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明無論是對小啪還是對我都是特別的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏要下雨啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰親…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個無比溫暖的聲音是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是小薰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今年又看不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為今年有爸爸在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有數不清的思念想傳達啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好多想說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我又開始拍照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這裡還交到了新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的東西  重要的事情在不斷增加著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮  好漂亮  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈籠也掛上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪寫的是給爸爸的問候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}麻音：想變成有作為的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}紀惠：想吃遍世界上的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}薰：果然大家的笑容最棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:28.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}楓：謝謝你教會了我那麼多\N  在天國也要保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:35.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}理穗：希望能夠更多更多地\N遇到現在還不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:40.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an7}昌子：與你經過的時間\N是我永遠的寶物  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是志保美小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機的畫好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  邊上的莫非是昌子小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是堂鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要在三分之內趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就提前收攤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:22:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要準備老師來幫忙的回禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有那個必要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長  一起去看祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是回禮的五層什錦燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什錦…燒～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望看到大家的笑容而拚命準備的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,款待我們的那些人們  期待這一天到來的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷揣著特別的回憶的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的人們的思念交織在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能看到與平日不同的這城市特別的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也多虧了小薰和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓今天成為了特別的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸的約定  似乎實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.37,0:24:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉響～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.47,0:24:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為是不變的人與漸漸變化的時光」
